expert Dave Ramsey&mdash;that incorporates small-group discussions to encourage accountability and discipleship.&nbsp;<em>Financial Peace University</em>&nbsp;is highly entertaining for everyone, with a unique combination of humor, informative financial advice and biblical messages. Dave's style is simple and easy to understand. He will change the way you think about money as you learn how to eliminate debt, build wealth and improve relationships. You'll actually have fun as you learn!</p><p>If you have already bought a kit from a previous class you do not have to repurchase materials.</p><p><a href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/eventlogin.aspx?id=6O0rNzNi1/g6E9JAxScFfQ==&amp;site=1233&amp;ReturnUrl=events%2fwz_people.aspx&amp;ChurchID=3183&amp;EventID=53488&amp;sn=1233" class="button">Register</a></p><hr><h3><br><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2277813&amp;fileName=graphic--staff-photo--ron-stokes-crop-0-0-200-300.jpg" width="200" height="300" alt="GRAPHIC : STAFF PHOTO : Ron Stokes - Crop" title="GRAPHIC : STAFF PHOTO : Ron Stokes - Crop" style="vertical-align: top;">Facilitator Info</h3><p class="class-intstructor-bio"><b>RON STOKES</b>&nbsp;is the Chief Stewardship Officer at Portland Christian Center. &nbsp;Ron has a broad depth of financial planning and financial services experience.</p><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><p>Follow/Contact Us: <a href="http://www.facebook.com/portlandchristiancenter" class="facebook" target="_blank">Facebook</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/pcctoday" class="twitter" target="_blank">Twitter</a> <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/lindanoah" class="linkedin"></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:lifelearning@pcctoday.com" class="email" target="_blank">Email</a>&nbsp;</p><h2 class="n"></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>